      "message": "[Major] Line 87: Adding host system pkg-config paths to PKG_CONFIG_PATH for all non-cross contrib builds can make need_pkg resolve against system libraries instead of the contrib prefix. That weakens reproducibility and can silently skip building required contrib versions depending on the developer machine. Prefer leaving PKG_CONFIG_PATH scoped to $(PREFIX), or gate system paths behind an explicit opt-in variable.",
