      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 2031: When a plugin previously produced no bodyOverwrite, this method does not record that the message was processed. Because loadMissingBodyOverwrites() treats absence of the key as missing work, every subsequent load/reload will re-run plugin transforms for the same messages forever. Store an explicit empty/sentinel value or otherwise distinguish \u0027processed with no overwrite\u0027 from \u0027not processed yet\u0027.",
      "revId": "6cf0f7e1ea8bad00a01b8ec3a5f53b76088e19db",
