      "writtenOn": "2026-05-29T16:21:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 2257: loadMissingBodyOverwrites() is called only after SwarmLoaded is emitted, so the loaded batch initially reaches clients without plugin body overwrites and is then corrected by later SwarmMessageUpdated signals. That contradicts the new ChatHandler API contract saying transforms happen before SwarmLoaded, and can cause visible flicker or stale rendering if clients do not merge follow-up updates for already-loaded rows. Run the transform before emitting SwarmLoaded, or update the API documentation to reflect asynchronous post-load updates.",
      "revId": "6cf0f7e1ea8bad00a01b8ec3a5f53b76088e19db",
